      "y": -820,
      "id": "08a3df7b382eaf0d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2820,
      "text": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "3f7b1f3592ad760a",
      "text": "Tomorrow morning, [[Isaac]] wanders in the town with no purpose and end up in the lavatory ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -754,
      "y": 1663,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 146,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "color": "1",
      "width": 250,
      "x": 6880,
      "height": 123,
      "text": "[[Lucas]] visits him multiple times trying to cheer him up but with no avail",
      "id": "fe3c79aa90827ac7",
      "y": 77,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "text": "[[Isaac]] pretends his excuse to come is to apologise for that he did ",
      "width": 250,
      "x": 6860,
      "id": "56db61f39b681861",
      "height": 125,
      "y": 479,
      "type": "text",
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "height": 84,
      "x": 7240,
      "color": "3",
      "type": "text",
      "id": "a4471654e1ff60e0",
      "width": 250,
      "y": 493,
      "text": "[[Cesare]], in a bath robe, reluctantly opens his door to him"
    },
    {
      "width": 250,
      "color": "1",
      "y": 860,
      "id": "eec24bee3337ae5d",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "[[Isaac]] apologize for his behavior and promises to not leak his secrets",
      "x": 7300,
      "height": 106
    },
    {
      "width": 285,
      "x": 6460,
      "type": "text",
      "y": -290,
      "text": "A week passes by without [[Isaac]] going to the church",
      "height": 80,
      "color": "1",
      "id": "38b712f25eff37b2"
    },
    {
      "width": 50,
      "text": "",
      "height": 50,
      "y": -275,
      "type": "text",
      "x": 6340,
      "id": "309e3d6127505c74"
    },
    {
      "height": 186,
      "x": 6478,
      "color": "2",
      "width": 250,
      "id": "3258f69f80ae0edf",
      "type": "text",
      "y": -16,
      "text": "he can't get out his what he felt back then when he takes photos of [[Cesare]] naked and when he got exposed to [his](Cesare) genitals"
    },
    {
      "width": 220,
      "height": 111,
      "id": "abeeb2f05e10180b",
      "text": "[[Isaac]] can't take it anymore and goes to [[Cesare]]'s house",
      "x": 6493,
      "y": 479,
      "type": "text",
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "id": "a9eeaddc2d383660",
      "text": "The [[Raincoat Man]] spies on their victim\n",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2080,
      "y": 632,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 60,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "width": 50,
      "y": 1832,
      "height": 50,
      "id": "541be7746489f5f8",
      "x": 2820,
      "text": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "",
      "id": "f06739443de366c0",
      "x": -1160,
      "y": 642,
      "width": 50,
      "height": 50,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "text": "",
      "type": "text",
      "id": "1adf31c620d52738",
      "x": -295,
      "y": -464,
      "width": 50,
      "height": 50,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "height": 50,
      "y": 1510,
      "x": 6340,
      "text": "",
      "id": "75d2cbf0dea6e44b",
      "width": 50,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "30c06c7a34d8747c",
      "text": "[[Isaac]] just finished moving into grandma's house",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -378,
      "y": -117,
      "width": 216,
      "height": 97,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "text": "",
      "type": "text",
      "id": "5ca8d0894e6f46ac",
      "x": -1160,
      "y": -464,
      "width": 50,
      "height": 50,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "He puts on a show by confessing of spying the new supporter ([[Isaac]]) in his intimate moments and that he doesn't regret it one bit",
      "height": 213,
      "x": 3820,
      "id": "37ca41d2144cc003",
      "color": "3",
      "width": 250,
      "y": 1138
    },
    {
      "text": "[[Cesare]] has to leave urgently because of a charity event.",
      "height": 108,
      "width": 250,
      "color": "3",
      "y": -448,
      "id": "f805b126dab32a91",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3960
    },
    {
      "text": "[[Isaac]] is frozen by fear but enjoys it",
      "width": 250,
      "id": "8e00240a3d9fc3eb",
      "x": 3080,
      "y": 2140,
      "type": "text",
      "color": "2",
      "height": 60
    },
    {
      "width": 250,
      "text": "[[Cesare]] notices that [[Isaac]] took photos of him naked and gets even more arroused",
      "height": 132,
      "type": "text",
      "id": "eb0bddf0405195b5",
      "color": "2",
      "y": 1839,
      "x": 3080
    },
    {
      "width": 250,
      "text": "After the confession, because of the exhaustion of the investigation, [[Isaac]] falls asleep in the confessional.",
      "x": 3741,
      "type": "text",
      "color": "1",
      "height": 189,
      "y": 144,
      "id": "967e5053fe4f7486"
    },
    {
      "text": "[[Cesare]] confesses to voyeurism",
      "height": 60,
      "x": 3220,
      "id": "3e5bbed6fa922c27",
      "color": "1",
      "width": 250,
      "type": "text",
      "y": 1214
    },
    {
