    },
    {
      "color": "#730c58",
      "height": 88,
      "width": 285,
      "x": 2024,
      "text": "Is this meant to be a plothook for later? - murkwater",
      "type": "text",
      "y": 1402,
      "id": "5c2fd423c44d7cc7"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "[[Isaac]] finds a camera and decides to take more photos to entertain himself.",
      "id": "a953d29f416d47ca",
      "x": -378,
      "y": 70,
      "width": 216,
      "height": 150,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "width": 400,
      "x": 2385,
      "id": "a12e96eed7e65bcc",
      "type": "file",
      "file": "Exhibitionist Priest/05 - Tasks/Pinned/Is the collective hallucination plot point pertinent to the story.md",
      "y": 1381,
      "height": 131,
      "color": "6"
    },
    {
      "x": 7710,
      "id": "d3c4d17368637241",
      "text": "Sure! - shin",
      "color": "6",
      "y": -777,
      "width": 250,
      "type": "text",
      "height": 60
    },
    {
      "text": "[[Simone]] finds him and tell him he should give a try to the local church",
      "type": "text",
      "id": "9fd7c1a26611d60b",
      "x": -1160,
      "y": 1220,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 129,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "text": "They play strip poker and [[Isaac]] pussies out last minute and the party ends on that",
      "type": "text",
      "id": "d22891dd4e957e40",
      "x": -370,
      "y": 1382,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 120,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "He proposes him to make him visit the church and they do",
      "id": "07e12c79e10c4137",
      "x": -380,
      "y": 2251,
      "width": 296,
      "height": 103,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "id": "7699975734aa5b8e",
      "text": "he also make him visit the lake",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 139,
      "y": 2274,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 60,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "a3b795f4dceaa384",
      "text": "[[Joseph]] is astonished with [[Cesare]]'s charisma",
      "x": -910,
      "y": 2019,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 60,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "6845fa97754f63df",
      "text": "[[Cesare]] is a smooth and seducing talker",
      "x": -910,
      "y": 2099,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 60,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "text": "[He](Cesare) reminds [him](Joseph) of his uncle",
      "type": "text",
      "id": "5f3c1fa6ce01de00",
      "x": -910,
      "y": 2191,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 60,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "she is a follower of the local church",
      "id": "1375babfc42cb8e9",
      "x": -1160,
      "y": 1548,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 60,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "672750f1357613c1",
      "text": "soft \"romantic\" scene",
      "x": 10,
      "y": 2117,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 60,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "id": "eb53508dd252208e",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "[[Joseph]] falls in love with him charm",
      "x": 301,
      "y": 2117,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 60,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "text": "[[Cesare]] already knows him given he spied on him in his house",
      "id": "f2273c44b648047b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -357,
      "y": 2400,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 106,
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "d90971df955a312e",
      "text": "[[Cesare]] sets his hook on him",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -70,
      "y": 2423,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 60,
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "she leads him to the church",
      "id": "bfce0d20b709e44e",
      "x": -1160,
      "y": 1421,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 60,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "text": "Hot scene for readers i guess lol. Also gambling games so foreshadowing of isaac in Cesare",
      "type": "text",
      "id": "7837f0a9fa426118",
      "x": 219,
      "y": 759,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 154,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "width": 250,
      "id": "c84752fc6f7f3d14",
      "x": -1715,
      "y": -2127,
      "height": 60,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "Cesare was born in a rich catholic family",
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "height": 107,
      "text": "got groomed under 10 by a member of his family more specifically a priest",
      "type": "text",
      "y": -2150,
      "x": -1380,
      "width": 312,
      "id": "985ef025c00c7aa9",
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "y": -2136,
      "color": "3",
      "height": 80,
      "text": "Tries to go into political science but ultimately drops out",
      "id": "097730e766ba6fc2",
      "x": -980,
      "width": 299
    },
    {
      "id": "2b2f823cc051f9c3",
      "type": "text",
      "y": -2300,
      "width": 250,
      "text": "Develops gambling and alcohol addictions",
      "x": -955,
      "color": "2",
      "height": 58
    },
    {
      "y": -1960,
      "color": "2",
      "x": -955,
      "id": "23667013acc1f87b",
      "width": 250,
      "type": "text",
      "height": 60,
      "text": "starts wanting to spy on other genitals"
    },
    {
      "height": 83,
      "text": "His family forces him to becoming a priest then a pastor to clear his family's name",
      "color": "3",
      "y": -2139,
      "x": -540,
      "id": "757bd24b17e596ea",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 340
    },
    {
      "text": "Thanks to his smooth talking abilities and his acts of generosity and charity (and his family status), he succeeds in becoming a pastor at a young age",
      "height": 149,
      "width": 340,
      "type": "text",
      "y": -2172,
      "id": "0868b55a1cb7008a",
      "x": -40,
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "width": 312,
      "y": -2392,
      "text": "the charity acts are just a way for him to cope with his troubled past",
      "color": "2",
      "type": "text",
      "height": 92,
      "x": -26,
      "id": "91f54c712ce183f8"
    },
    {
      "color": "2",
      "height": 141,
      "text": "He has more and more trouble containing his voyeuristic and exhibitionist and urges and acts on them",
      "x": -17,
      "id": "bfc7a2323bc527e8",
      "y": -1940,
      "type": "text",
      "width": 295
    },
    {
      "width": 277,
      "text": "He got caught masturbating on a late night jogger",
      "type": "text",
      "y": -2139,
      "height": 84,
      "color": "3",
      "x": 460,
      "id": "96c49b28692ab1fd"
    },
    {
      "height": 93,
      "text": "Thanks to his family, he was able to get out of it without a criminal case",
      "id": "1a853734bbf4f496",
      "x": 820,
      "width": 289,
      "type": "text",
      "color": "3",
      "y": -2144
    },
    {
      "id": "5bd7c650571aa5ef",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "He hears about Isaac's coming because of they are neighbors and starts developing an obsession on him",
      "x": 1220,
      "y": -2160,
      "width": 360,
      "height": 127,
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "id": "00c87d436e6b0059",
      "type": "group",
      "x": -1735,
      "y": -2412,
      "width": 3335,
      "height": 752,
      "color": "4",
      "label": "Cesare's backstory"
    },
    {
      "color": "2",
      "y": 940,
      "text": "[[Isaac]] mistakenly fantasises about [[Lucas]] betting his underwear away and only wearing a top",
      "type": "text",
      "height": 78,
      "width": 402,
      "id": "e3178d074bc8d155",
      "x": 143
    },
    {
      "id": "c6f62b71f7028355",
      "x": -1349,
      "y": -2302,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 60,
      "color": "2",
