    },
    {
      "id": "3f7b1f3592ad760a",
      "text": "Tomorrow morning, [[Isaac]] wanders in the town with no purpose and end up in the lavatory ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -754,
      "y": 1663,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 146,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "color": "1",
      "width": 250,
      "x": 6880,
      "height": 123,
      "text": "[[Lucas]] visits him multiple times trying to cheer him up but with no avail",
      "id": "fe3c79aa90827ac7",
      "y": 77,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "text": "[[Isaac]] pretends his excuse to come is to apologise for that he did ",
      "width": 250,
      "x": 6860,
      "id": "56db61f39b681861",
      "height": 125,
      "y": 479,
      "type": "text",
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "height": 84,
      "x": 7240,
      "color": "3",
      "type": "text",
      "id": "a4471654e1ff60e0",
      "width": 250,
      "y": 493,
      "text": "[[Cesare]], in a bath robe, reluctantly opens his door to him"
    },
    {
      "width": 250,
      "color": "1",
      "y": 860,
      "id": "eec24bee3337ae5d",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "[[Isaac]] apologize for his behavior and promises to not leak his secrets",
      "x": 7300,
      "height": 106
    },
    {
      "width": 285,
      "x": 6460,
      "type": "text",
      "y": -290,
      "text": "A week passes by without [[Isaac]] going to the church",
      "height": 80,
      "color": "1",
      "id": "38b712f25eff37b2"
    },
    {
      "width": 50,
      "text": "",
      "height": 50,
      "y": -275,
      "type": "text",
      "x": 6340,
      "id": "309e3d6127505c74"
    },
    {
      "height": 186,
      "x": 6478,
      "color": "2",
      "width": 250,
      "id": "3258f69f80ae0edf",
      "type": "text",
      "y": -16,
      "text": "he can't get out his what he felt back then when he takes photos of [[Cesare]] naked and when he got exposed to [his](Cesare) genitals"
    },
    {
      "width": 220,
      "height": 111,
      "id": "abeeb2f05e10180b",
      "text": "[[Isaac]] can't take it anymore and goes to [[Cesare]]'s house",
      "x": 6493,
      "y": 479,
      "type": "text",
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "id": "a9eeaddc2d383660",
      "text": "The [[Raincoat Man]] spies on their victim\n",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2080,
      "y": 632,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 60,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "width": 50,
      "y": 1832,
      "height": 50,
      "id": "541be7746489f5f8",
      "x": 2820,
