      "x": 6340,
      "text": "",
      "id": "75d2cbf0dea6e44b",
      "width": 50,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "30c06c7a34d8747c",
      "text": "[[Isaac]] just finished moving into grandma's house",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -378,
      "y": -117,
      "width": 216,
      "height": 97,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "text": "",
      "type": "text",
      "id": "5ca8d0894e6f46ac",
      "x": -1160,
      "y": -464,
      "width": 50,
      "height": 50,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "He puts on a show by confessing of spying the new supporter ([[Isaac]]) in his intimate moments and that he doesn't regret it one bit",
      "height": 213,
      "x": 3820,
      "id": "37ca41d2144cc003",
      "color": "3",
      "width": 250,
      "y": 1138
    },
    {
      "text": "[[Cesare]] has to leave urgently because of a charity event.",
      "height": 108,
      "width": 250,
      "color": "3",
      "y": -448,
      "id": "f805b126dab32a91",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3960
    },
    {
      "text": "[[Isaac]] is frozen by fear but enjoys it",
      "width": 250,
      "id": "8e00240a3d9fc3eb",
      "x": 3080,
      "y": 2140,
      "type": "text",
      "color": "2",
      "height": 60
    },
    {
      "width": 250,
      "text": "[[Cesare]] notices that [[Isaac]] took photos of him naked and gets even more arroused",
      "height": 132,
      "type": "text",
      "id": "eb0bddf0405195b5",
      "color": "2",
      "y": 1839,
      "x": 3080
    },
    {
      "width": 250,
      "text": "After the confession, because of the exhaustion of the investigation, [[Isaac]] falls asleep in the confessional.",
      "x": 3741,
      "type": "text",
      "color": "1",
      "height": 189,
      "y": 144,
      "id": "967e5053fe4f7486"
    },
    {
      "text": "[[Cesare]] confesses to voyeurism",
      "height": 60,
      "x": 3220,
      "id": "3e5bbed6fa922c27",
      "color": "1",
      "width": 250,
      "type": "text",
      "y": 1214
    },
    {
      "id": "989c5179bb5ddf9d",
      "text": "[[Cesare]], after the ecstasy, realizes what he did and thinks of what he can do after the confession. The other priest leaves",
      "height": 175,
      "color": "3",
      "x": 3275,
      "type": "text",
      "y": 1420,
      "width": 250
    },
    {
      "height": 310,
      "type": "text",
      "color": "3",
      "width": 250,
      "y": 84,
      "text": "But he gets urges to do something bad with [[Isaac]] so he tries to confess to the other priest on site but realizes he's gonna enter in [[Isaac]]'s booth. He hopes he'll be gone as he can't tell he let someone in the confessionals",
      "x": 2900,
      "id": "c31fc6dbee9bce4c"
    },
    {
      "text": "[[Cesare]] notices [[Isaac]] hiding. He gets a crazy idea. He promptly removes his underwear and goes sit in the booth to expose his genitals",
      "y": 771,
      "color": "3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3062,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 204,
      "id": "0ff325d459dcc4c8"
    },
    {
      "y": 1710,
      "x": 3080,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 60,
      "id": "0ce1a506185f03e6",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "[[Cesare]] keeps the camera to blackmail him",
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "height": 229,
      "color": "3",
      "y": -509,
      "width": 250,
      "id": "020aeceac6b0b2d4",
      "text": "[[Cesare]] had decided to jerk off to his confession at first but realizing [[Isaac]] and him are more similar than they think, he starts to relate to [[Isaac]] even ",
      "x": 3616,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "89a994ca9e2f10a0",
      "y": -127,
      "x": 3614,
      "text": "[[Cesare]] thinks they might be kindred souls",
      "height": 60,
      "color": "3",
      "width": 250,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "x": 3100,
      "height": 229,
      "text": "[[Isaac]] lies about committing regularly [[exhibitionism]] and [[voyeurism]] but ends up really confessing about his uncertainty about the future and his lack of purpose",
      "color": "1",
      "type": "text",
      "id": "dc4c4b38feb33153",
      "width": 250,
      "y": -509
    },
    {
      "height": 80,
      "id": "b836614a1c041361",
