      "width": 250,
      "id": "79778b1457f38528",
      "text": "After a breakdown, [[Isaac]] admits he's been lying about the confessions ([[voyeurism]] and [[exhibitionism]]) and reveals snooping about him",
      "height": 200
    },
    {
      "height": 60,
      "width": 250,
      "type": "text",
      "color": "1",
      "text": "[[Isaac]] discusses with [[Cesare]] about the photos",
      "id": "a53758a0a3948d96",
      "x": 4680,
      "y": 781
    },
    {
      "height": 96,
      "id": "bd36f66a531c1de4",
      "text": "[[Cesare]] proposes [him](Isaac) to become his partner and explore those urges",
      "width": 250,
      "type": "text",
      "color": "3",
      "x": 5100,
      "y": 840
    },
    {
      "height": 344,
      "y": 67,
      "x": 3364,
      "text": "When [[Cesare]] comes back late of his event to the church to check the last requirements to close the church for the night, he notices [[Isaac]] sleeping in the booth. He gets the idea to wake him up after he's done with his work and propose him to become his partner.",
      "width": 250,
      "id": "ff28b65e6542e093",
      "type": "text",
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "y": 193,
      "id": "6d50eb23a1c11814",
      "type": "text",
      "color": "2",
      "height": 94,
      "width": 250,
      "text": "[[Joseph]] couldn't follow [him](Cesare) at the time",
      "x": 1845
    },
    {
      "text": "[He](Cesare) is friend with the [owner](Jeff)",
      "y": 97,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 60,
      "type": "text",
      "color": "2",
      "id": "be987165b87d23bc",
      "x": 1845
    },
    {
      "color": "3",
      "text": "[[Cesare]] is delighted that he'll be able to know [[Isaac]]'s secret",
      "height": 97,
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2085,
      "y": 1808,
      "id": "1bb0a045c5ca49fd",
      "width": 250
    },
    {
      "id": "6eabb8900d447c25",
      "y": 489,
      "type": "text",
      "height": 60,
      "color": "1",
      "x": 5140,
      "width": 250,
      "text": "[[Isaac]] goes to the café"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "height": 178,
      "text": "[[Cesare]] takes advantage of the situation for coming back on [his](Isaac) confessions asking [[Isaac]] questions about faith and life morals",
      "y": 603,
      "color": "3",
      "id": "280d8e71f341c34e",
      "width": 250,
      "x": 5100
    },
    {
      "x": 5480,
      "width": 250,
      "text": "[[Cesare]] is devastated and disillusioned. His only hope of meeting someone similar just shattered. At this moment, he gives up on his church life and accept his fate",
      "color": "3",
      "height": 226,
      "id": "66ff87488a3431b1",
      "type": "text",
      "y": 1224
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "width": 250,
      "x": 5078,
      "color": "1",
      "text": "[[Cesare]] throws the camera at him and tells him he can do whatever with it",
      "height": 122,
      "id": "e5193bd5f15828f9",
      "y": 1278
    },
    {
      "width": 250,
      "height": 60,
      "x": 5140,
      "y": -550,
      "id": "560959f1a391bfb5",
      "color": "2",
      "text": "[[Isaac]] wonders how he got his address",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "y": -600,
      "height": 160,
      "id": "6bd6a50f4a4638d1",
      "color": "1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4680,
      "text": "[[Cesare]] drops [[Isaac]] off at his home and gives him a rendez vous at the café in exchange of the camera",
      "width": 250
    },
    {
      "text": "[[Lucas]] is worried about [[Isaac]] and decides to go there tomorrow even though he was told not to ",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 250,
      "y": 180,
      "x": 5140,
      "height": 160,
      "color": "2",
      "id": "39ed3672daf9e53c"
    },
    {
      "x": 5140,
      "y": -58,
      "type": "text",
      "width": 250,
      "height": 184,
      "color": "2",
      "text": "[[Isaac]] gets angry about his incompetence and that he couldn't do anything about Cesare and wants to fix it alone",
      "id": "10ba57734d6f533e"
    },
    {
      "color": "1",
      "width": 250,
      "id": "7450bfd359f0bec8",
      "x": 5140,
      "text": "[[Isaac]] can't sleep so he calls [[Lucas]] over",
      "height": 60,
      "type": "text",
      "y": -260
    },
    {
      "height": 101,
      "x": 1029,
      "width": 250,
      "text": "Infiltrated at the police station, he looks at [[Cesare]]'s file",
      "id": "a6be10d85ce2db8b",
      "color": "1",
      "type": "text",
      "y": 1520
    },
    {
      "id": "b0d33ce524fd10b0",
      "text": "[[Joseph]] goes to the café and talks with the [owner](Jeff)",
      "color": "1",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 250,
      "height": 84,
      "x": 1029,
      "y": 821
    },
    {
      "color": "2",
      "text": "[He](Cesare) has no criminal record.",
      "width": 250,
      "height": 60,
      "id": "2b8a8f4432953eff",
      "x": 1720,
      "y": 1460,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "text": "With this new lead, [[Joseph]] convinces [[Nick]] to let him infiltrate the police station.",
      "x": 1744,
      "type": "text",
      "y": 1220,
      "color": "1",
      "height": 120,
      "id": "30c83480d1bfcd03",
      "width": 250
    },
    {
      "x": 4680,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "[[Isaac]] tells [[Lucas]] he's getting blackmailed by [[Cesare]] and has to meet him tomorrow. [[Lucas]] sleeps here..",
      "width": 250,
      "color": "1",
      "id": "39a2460bdf0cbda1",
      "y": 51,
      "height": 149
    },
    {
      "y": 1508,
      "x": 700,
      "width": 50,
      "id": "4103a36951170e28",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "",
      "height": 50
    },
    {
      "id": "4f412317308c7358",
      "text": "[[Joseph]] meets [[Cesare]]",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -856,
      "y": 1943,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 60,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "id": "fecd6dc0231f1de1",
      "color": "1",
      "width": 250,
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1744,
      "text": "[[Isaac]] hears gossip in the church about [[Cesare]]",
      "y": -120,
      "height": 60
    },
    {
      "id": "70625a4dd3494c1e",
      "color": "2",
      "x": 1494,
      "type": "text",
      "height": 60,
      "y": 97,
      "text": "[[Cesare]] goes to the [café-museum](Café)",
      "width": 250
    },
    {
      "id": "bcafc0159eb95962",
      "color": "1",
      "y": 120,
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1029,
      "text": "[[Isaac]] follows [[Cesare]] around, take pictures, jolts down the places [he](Cesare) frequents",
      "height": 120,
      "width": 250
    },
    {
      "text": "[Owner](Jeff) hints at [[Isaac]] that [he](Cesare) has been caught jerking off to a late night jogger in the parking lot and advises him to back off [[Cesare]] for his own sake",
      "height": 225,
      "type": "text",
      "y": 756,
      "x": 1404,
      "color": "2",
      "width": 250,
      "id": "b912acd7aac7dfa0"
    },
    {
      "x": 1279,
      "text": "[[Joseph]] notices they are neighbours",
      "color": "2",
      "height": 60,
      "id": "45fc7f4e518c2383",
      "y": 604,
      "type": "text",
      "width": 250
    },
    {
      "x": 1744,
      "type": "text",
      "height": 134,
      "id": "c229ff5210cdffe6",
      "text": "[[Isaac]] follows [[Cesare]] home and takes pictures of [him](Cesare) naked by mistake",
      "y": 500,
      "width": 250,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "text": "[[Joseph]] can't bring himself down to delete the photos (commit [[voyeurism]])",
      "id": "6dc74dc2ea3cc750",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1279,
      "y": 443,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 114,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "y": 1840,
      "width": 50,
      "height": 50,
      "text": "",
      "x": 4210,
      "id": "8811e124b8068676",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "f42321ec688b7f50",
      "y": 193,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "[[Cesare]] takes his car and drives for the closest city",
      "x": 1494,
      "color": "2",
      "width": 250,
      "height": 94
    },
    {
      "width": 250,
      "y": 1808,
      "x": 1744,
      "type": "text",
      "id": "be5fd311fc48df6d",
      "text": "[[Isaac]] pretends to confess to [[Cesare]] to gain information",
      "height": 97,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "color": "2",
      "y": 1535,
      "text": "[[Isaac]] stumbles upon another case, that of a night of collective hallucination.",
      "x": 1720,
      "id": "fc6846a032142b87",
      "height": 120,
      "type": "text",
      "width": 250
    },
    {
      "y": -360,
      "height": 80,
      "type": "text",
      "color": "1",
      "id": "3e31ec810812e7b7",
      "width": 250,
      "text": "[[Joseph]] obsesses over [[Cesare]]",
      "x": 1029
    },
    {
      "text": "",
      "id": "923acb02d83e4238",
      "height": 50,
      "width": 50,
      "x": 720,
      "type": "text",
      "y": -350
    },
    {
      "x": 4380,
      "type": "text",
      "id": "85e00043c3d388d3",
      "height": 94,
      "width": 230,
      "y": 764,
      "text": "[[Lucas]] is undercover listening to the discussion",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "0748736014548f5d",
      "y": 466,
      "color": "5",
      "height": 104,
      "x": 4555,
      "text": "[[Lucas]] wasn't here anymore when [[Isaac]] woke up",
      "width": 250
    },
    {
      "height": 50,
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4230,
      "text": "",
      "y": -545,
      "id": "34fae018f8df4e70",
      "width": 50
    },
    {
      "y": 1520,
      "height": 55,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "",
      "x": 5172,
      "id": "572e14fc790b5720",
      "width": 62
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3720,
      "text": "[[Isaac]], in a panic, hides under the seat and closes his eyes from fear.",
      "y": 747,
      "color": "1",
      "id": "4a9cc2c86b1dce10",
      "width": 250,
      "height": 126
    },
    {
      "text": "[[Isaac]] drops the coffee on purpose and as [[Cesare]] cleans up the mess, [[Isaac]] takes a pic of his genitals",
      "y": 1170,
      "height": 160,
      "color": "1",
      "width": 250,
      "type": "text",
      "id": "c49b521473c8c338",
      "x": 6540
    },
    {
      "height": 160,
      "type": "text",
      "width": 250,
      "id": "bf45ce2abe929050",
      "text": "They make up  and realize they might be more similar than they thought and decide to become partner in crime",
      "x": 7340,
      "y": 1530,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "width": 250,
      "id": "3a5491b3c9fb6788",
      "text": "[[Cesare]] does not find the force to go to the church and pretends to be sick",
      "x": 6478,
      "height": 122,
      "y": -500,
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "x": 6540,
      "y": 807,
      "width": 250,
      "id": "8d673242005669e4",
      "color": "2",
      "height": 106,
      "text": "[[Isaac]] tries to give the camera to [[Cesare]] but he refuses",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "text": "[[Cesare]] proposes and get to [[Isaac]] a coffee",
      "color": "3",
      "type": "text",
      "height": 60,
      "y": 936,
      "x": 6540,
      "id": "3043f2ad22451782",
      "width": 250
    },
    {
      "height": 106,
      "y": 1197,
      "id": "f51efa81dd0b0c92",
      "color": "3",
      "text": "[[Cesare]] gets really mad at [[Isaac]], grabs him and yells at him",
      "width": 250,
      "type": "text",
      "x": 7020
    },
    {
      "width": 250,
      "height": 60,
      "text": "Camera shatters on the ground",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 7425,
      "y": 1100,
      "color": "2",
      "id": "3a44141c093ff30a"
    },
    {
      "x": 7425,
      "height": 219,
      "text": "[[Isaac]] breaks down and admits he liked when [[Cesare]] exposed his genitals to him and when he took a pic of [him](Cesare) naked and wants to feel it again",
      "type": "text",
      "color": "2",
      "y": 1210,
      "id": "5d70ac58e8128623",
      "width": 250
    },
    {
      "y": -820,
      "height": 50,
      "width": 50,
      "id": "517b1cfe3ace7517",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "",
      "x": 3716
    },
