    },
    {
      "id": "3f7b1f3592ad760a",
      "text": "Tomorrow morning, [[Isaac]] wanders in the town with no purpose and end up in the lavatory ",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -754,
      "y": 1663,
      "width": 280,
      "height": 146,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "color": "1",
      "width": 250,
      "x": 6880,
      "height": 123,
      "text": "[[Lucas]] visits him multiple times trying to cheer him up but with no avail",
      "id": "fe3c79aa90827ac7",
      "y": 77,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "text": "[[Isaac]] pretends his excuse to come is to apologise for that he did ",
      "width": 250,
      "x": 6860,
      "id": "56db61f39b681861",
      "height": 125,
      "y": 479,
      "type": "text",
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "height": 84,
      "x": 7240,
      "color": "3",
      "type": "text",
      "id": "a4471654e1ff60e0",
      "width": 250,
      "y": 493,
      "text": "[[Cesare]], in a bath robe, reluctantly opens his door to him"
    },
    {
      "width": 250,
      "color": "1",
      "y": 860,
      "id": "eec24bee3337ae5d",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "[[Isaac]] apologize for his behavior and promises to not leak his secrets",
      "x": 7300,
      "height": 106
    },
    {
      "width": 285,
      "x": 6460,
      "type": "text",
      "y": -290,
      "text": "A week passes by without [[Isaac]] going to the church",
      "height": 80,
      "color": "1",
      "id": "38b712f25eff37b2"
    },
    {
      "width": 50,
      "text": "",
      "height": 50,
      "y": -275,
      "type": "text",
      "x": 6340,
      "id": "309e3d6127505c74"
    },
    {
      "height": 186,
      "x": 6478,
      "color": "2",
      "width": 250,
      "id": "3258f69f80ae0edf",
      "type": "text",
      "y": -16,
      "text": "he can't get out his what he felt back then when he takes photos of [[Cesare]] naked and when he got exposed to [his](Cesare) genitals"
    },
    {
      "width": 220,
      "height": 111,
      "id": "abeeb2f05e10180b",
      "text": "[[Isaac]] can't take it anymore and goes to [[Cesare]]'s house",
      "x": 6493,
      "y": 479,
      "type": "text",
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "id": "a9eeaddc2d383660",
      "text": "The [[Raincoat Man]] spies on their victim\n",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -2080,
      "y": 632,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 60,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "width": 50,
      "y": 1832,
      "height": 50,
      "id": "541be7746489f5f8",
      "x": 2820,
      "text": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "",
      "id": "f06739443de366c0",
      "x": -1160,
      "y": 642,
      "width": 50,
      "height": 50,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "text": "",
      "type": "text",
      "id": "1adf31c620d52738",
      "x": -295,
      "y": -464,
      "width": 50,
      "height": 50,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "height": 50,
      "y": 1510,
      "x": 6340,
      "text": "",
      "id": "75d2cbf0dea6e44b",
      "width": 50,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "30c06c7a34d8747c",
      "text": "[[Isaac]] just finished moving into grandma's house",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -378,
      "y": -117,
      "width": 216,
      "height": 97,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "text": "",
      "type": "text",
      "id": "5ca8d0894e6f46ac",
      "x": -1160,
      "y": -464,
      "width": 50,
      "height": 50,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "text": "He puts on a show by confessing of spying the new supporter ([[Isaac]]) in his intimate moments and that he doesn't regret it one bit",
      "height": 213,
      "x": 3820,
      "id": "37ca41d2144cc003",
      "color": "3",
      "width": 250,
      "y": 1138
    },
    {
      "text": "[[Cesare]] has to leave urgently because of a charity event.",
      "height": 108,
      "width": 250,
      "color": "3",
      "y": -448,
      "id": "f805b126dab32a91",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3960
    },
    {
      "text": "[[Isaac]] is frozen by fear but enjoys it",
      "width": 250,
      "id": "8e00240a3d9fc3eb",
      "x": 3080,
      "y": 2140,
      "type": "text",
      "color": "2",
      "height": 60
    },
    {
      "width": 250,
      "text": "[[Cesare]] notices that [[Isaac]] took photos of him naked and gets even more arroused",
      "height": 132,
      "type": "text",
      "id": "eb0bddf0405195b5",
      "color": "2",
      "y": 1839,
      "x": 3080
    },
    {
      "width": 250,
      "text": "After the confession, because of the exhaustion of the investigation, [[Isaac]] falls asleep in the confessional.",
      "x": 3741,
      "type": "text",
      "color": "1",
      "height": 189,
      "y": 144,
      "id": "967e5053fe4f7486"
    },
    {
      "text": "[[Cesare]] confesses to voyeurism",
      "height": 60,
      "x": 3220,
      "id": "3e5bbed6fa922c27",
      "color": "1",
      "width": 250,
      "type": "text",
      "y": 1214
    },
    {
      "id": "989c5179bb5ddf9d",
      "text": "[[Cesare]], after the ecstasy, realizes what he did and thinks of what he can do after the confession. The other priest leaves",
      "height": 175,
      "color": "3",
      "x": 3275,
      "type": "text",
      "y": 1420,
      "width": 250
    },
    {
      "height": 310,
      "type": "text",
      "color": "3",
      "width": 250,
      "y": 84,
      "text": "But he gets urges to do something bad with [[Isaac]] so he tries to confess to the other priest on site but realizes he's gonna enter in [[Isaac]]'s booth. He hopes he'll be gone as he can't tell he let someone in the confessionals",
      "x": 2900,
      "id": "c31fc6dbee9bce4c"
    },
    {
      "text": "[[Cesare]] notices [[Isaac]] hiding. He gets a crazy idea. He promptly removes his underwear and goes sit in the booth to expose his genitals",
      "y": 771,
      "color": "3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3062,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 204,
      "id": "0ff325d459dcc4c8"
    },
    {
      "y": 1710,
      "x": 3080,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 60,
      "id": "0ce1a506185f03e6",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "[[Cesare]] keeps the camera to blackmail him",
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "height": 229,
      "color": "3",
      "y": -509,
      "width": 250,
      "id": "020aeceac6b0b2d4",
      "text": "[[Cesare]] had decided to jerk off to his confession at first but realizing [[Isaac]] and him are more similar than they think, he starts to relate to [[Isaac]] even ",
      "x": 3616,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "89a994ca9e2f10a0",
      "y": -127,
      "x": 3614,
      "text": "[[Cesare]] thinks they might be kindred souls",
      "height": 60,
      "color": "3",
      "width": 250,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "x": 3100,
      "height": 229,
      "text": "[[Isaac]] lies about committing regularly [[exhibitionism]] and [[voyeurism]] but ends up really confessing about his uncertainty about the future and his lack of purpose",
      "color": "1",
      "type": "text",
      "id": "dc4c4b38feb33153",
      "width": 250,
      "y": -509
    },
    {
      "height": 80,
      "id": "b836614a1c041361",
      "y": 27,
      "type": "file",
      "file": "Exhibitionist Priest/02 - Attachments/Icons/shush.png",
      "x": 3100,
      "width": 80
    },
    {
      "width": 250,
      "type": "text",
      "color": "2",
      "height": 88,
      "text": "Maybe he forgets about [[Joseph]] while he gets horny",
      "x": 2900,
      "id": "0568665184d68241",
      "y": -171
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "width": 250,
      "x": 3695,
      "y": 1751,
      "text": "[[Cesare]] gets [[Isaac]] and blackmail him by using his camera to take a compromising photo of him his dick dangling (exhibitionism for [[Isaac]])",
      "color": "1",
      "id": "8c2864190ae2d38e",
      "height": 220
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3062,
      "color": "1",
      "height": 146,
      "text": "[[Isaac]] wakes up at the sound of footsteps and voices and see that Cesare is about to enter in the booth",
      "width": 250,
      "y": 528,
      "id": "0165ab24c0349c1f"
    },
    {
      "y": 1832,
      "id": "ccdec5fd1c5ea652",
      "x": 2720,
      "height": 50,
      "text": "",
      "width": 50,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "text": "",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 50,
      "y": -419,
      "id": "4a34d7224f937b61",
      "height": 50,
      "x": 2720
    },
    {
      "y": 980,
      "type": "text",
      "color": "2",
      "x": 5100,
      "width": 250,
      "id": "79778b1457f38528",
      "text": "After a breakdown, [[Isaac]] admits he's been lying about the confessions ([[voyeurism]] and [[exhibitionism]]) and reveals snooping about him",
      "height": 200
    },
    {
      "height": 60,
      "width": 250,
      "type": "text",
      "color": "1",
      "text": "[[Isaac]] discusses with [[Cesare]] about the photos",
      "id": "a53758a0a3948d96",
      "x": 4680,
      "y": 781
    },
    {
      "height": 96,
      "id": "bd36f66a531c1de4",
      "text": "[[Cesare]] proposes [him](Isaac) to become his partner and explore those urges",
      "width": 250,
      "type": "text",
      "color": "3",
      "x": 5100,
      "y": 840
    },
    {
      "height": 344,
      "y": 67,
      "x": 3364,
      "text": "When [[Cesare]] comes back late of his event to the church to check the last requirements to close the church for the night, he notices [[Isaac]] sleeping in the booth. He gets the idea to wake him up after he's done with his work and propose him to become his partner.",
      "width": 250,
      "id": "ff28b65e6542e093",
      "type": "text",
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "y": 193,
      "id": "6d50eb23a1c11814",
      "type": "text",
      "color": "2",
      "height": 94,
      "width": 250,
      "text": "[[Joseph]] couldn't follow [him](Cesare) at the time",
      "x": 1845
    },
    {
      "text": "[He](Cesare) is friend with the [owner](Jeff)",
      "y": 97,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 60,
      "type": "text",
      "color": "2",
      "id": "be987165b87d23bc",
      "x": 1845
    },
    {
      "color": "3",
      "text": "[[Cesare]] is delighted that he'll be able to know [[Isaac]]'s secret",
      "height": 97,
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2085,
      "y": 1808,
      "id": "1bb0a045c5ca49fd",
      "width": 250
    },
    {
      "id": "6eabb8900d447c25",
      "y": 489,
      "type": "text",
      "height": 60,
      "color": "1",
      "x": 5140,
      "width": 250,
      "text": "[[Isaac]] goes to the café"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "height": 178,
      "text": "[[Cesare]] takes advantage of the situation for coming back on [his](Isaac) confessions asking [[Isaac]] questions about faith and life morals",
      "y": 603,
      "color": "3",
      "id": "280d8e71f341c34e",
      "width": 250,
      "x": 5100
    },
    {
      "x": 5480,
      "width": 250,
      "text": "[[Cesare]] is devastated and disillusioned. His only hope of meeting someone similar just shattered. At this moment, he gives up on his church life and accept his fate",
      "color": "3",
      "height": 226,
      "id": "66ff87488a3431b1",
      "type": "text",
      "y": 1224
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "width": 250,
      "x": 5078,
      "color": "1",
      "text": "[[Cesare]] throws the camera at him and tells him he can do whatever with it",
      "height": 122,
      "id": "e5193bd5f15828f9",
      "y": 1278
    },
    {
      "width": 250,
      "height": 60,
      "x": 5140,
      "y": -550,
      "id": "560959f1a391bfb5",
      "color": "2",
      "text": "[[Isaac]] wonders how he got his address",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "y": -600,
      "height": 160,
      "id": "6bd6a50f4a4638d1",
      "color": "1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4680,
      "text": "[[Cesare]] drops [[Isaac]] off at his home and gives him a rendez vous at the café in exchange of the camera",
      "width": 250
    },
    {
      "text": "[[Lucas]] is worried about [[Isaac]] and decides to go there tomorrow even though he was told not to ",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 250,
      "y": 180,
      "x": 5140,
      "height": 160,
      "color": "2",
      "id": "39ed3672daf9e53c"
    },
    {
      "x": 5140,
      "y": -58,
      "type": "text",
      "width": 250,
      "height": 184,
      "color": "2",
      "text": "[[Isaac]] gets angry about his incompetence and that he couldn't do anything about Cesare and wants to fix it alone",
      "id": "10ba57734d6f533e"
    },
    {
      "color": "1",
      "width": 250,
      "id": "7450bfd359f0bec8",
      "x": 5140,
      "text": "[[Isaac]] can't sleep so he calls [[Lucas]] over",
      "height": 60,
      "type": "text",
      "y": -260
    },
    {
      "height": 101,
      "x": 1029,
      "width": 250,
      "text": "Infiltrated at the police station, he looks at [[Cesare]]'s file",
      "id": "a6be10d85ce2db8b",
      "color": "1",
      "type": "text",
      "y": 1520
    },
    {
      "id": "b0d33ce524fd10b0",
      "text": "[[Joseph]] goes to the café and talks with the [owner](Jeff)",
      "color": "1",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 250,
      "height": 84,
      "x": 1029,
      "y": 821
    },
    {
      "color": "2",
      "text": "[He](Cesare) has no criminal record.",
      "width": 250,
      "height": 60,
      "id": "2b8a8f4432953eff",
      "x": 1720,
      "y": 1460,
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "text": "With this new lead, [[Joseph]] convinces [[Nick]] to let him infiltrate the police station.",
      "x": 1744,
      "type": "text",
      "y": 1220,
      "color": "1",
      "height": 120,
      "id": "30c83480d1bfcd03",
      "width": 250
    },
    {
      "x": 4680,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "[[Isaac]] tells [[Lucas]] he's getting blackmailed by [[Cesare]] and has to meet him tomorrow. [[Lucas]] sleeps here..",
      "width": 250,
      "color": "1",
      "id": "39a2460bdf0cbda1",
      "y": 51,
      "height": 149
    },
    {
      "y": 1508,
      "x": 700,
      "width": 50,
      "id": "4103a36951170e28",
      "type": "text",
      "text": "",
      "height": 50
    },
    {
      "id": "4f412317308c7358",
      "text": "[[Joseph]] meets [[Cesare]]",
      "type": "text",
      "x": -856,
      "y": 1943,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 60,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "id": "fecd6dc0231f1de1",
      "color": "1",
      "width": 250,
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1744,
      "text": "[[Isaac]] hears gossip in the church about [[Cesare]]",
      "y": -120,
      "height": 60
    },
    {
      "id": "70625a4dd3494c1e",
      "color": "2",
      "x": 1494,
      "type": "text",
      "height": 60,
      "y": 97,
      "text": "[[Cesare]] goes to the [café-museum](Café)",
      "width": 250
    },
    {
      "id": "bcafc0159eb95962",
      "color": "1",
      "y": 120,
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1029,
      "text": "[[Isaac]] follows [[Cesare]] around, take pictures, jolts down the places [he](Cesare) frequents",
      "height": 120,
      "width": 250
    },
    {
      "text": "[Owner](Jeff) hints at [[Isaac]] that [he](Cesare) has been caught jerking off to a late night jogger in the parking lot and advises him to back off [[Cesare]] for his own sake",
      "height": 225,
      "type": "text",
      "y": 756,
      "x": 1404,
      "color": "2",
      "width": 250,
      "id": "b912acd7aac7dfa0"
    },
    {
      "x": 1279,
      "text": "[[Joseph]] notices they are neighbours",
      "color": "2",
      "height": 60,
      "id": "45fc7f4e518c2383",
      "y": 604,
      "type": "text",
      "width": 250
    },
    {
      "x": 1744,
      "type": "text",
      "height": 134,
      "id": "c229ff5210cdffe6",
      "text": "[[Isaac]] follows [[Cesare]] home and takes pictures of [him](Cesare) naked by mistake",
      "y": 500,
      "width": 250,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "text": "[[Joseph]] can't bring himself down to delete the photos (commit [[voyeurism]])",
      "id": "6dc74dc2ea3cc750",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1279,
      "y": 443,
      "width": 250,
      "height": 114,
      "color": "2"
    },
    {
      "y": 1840,
      "width": 50,
      "height": 50,
      "text": "",
      "x": 4210,
      "id": "8811e124b8068676",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "id": "f42321ec688b7f50",
      "y": 193,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "[[Cesare]] takes his car and drives for the closest city",
      "x": 1494,
      "color": "2",
      "width": 250,
      "height": 94
    },
    {
      "width": 250,
      "y": 1808,
      "x": 1744,
      "type": "text",
      "id": "be5fd311fc48df6d",
      "text": "[[Isaac]] pretends to confess to [[Cesare]] to gain information",
      "height": 97,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "color": "2",
      "y": 1535,
      "text": "[[Isaac]] stumbles upon another case, that of a night of collective hallucination.",
      "x": 1720,
      "id": "fc6846a032142b87",
      "height": 120,
      "type": "text",
      "width": 250
    },
    {
      "y": -360,
      "height": 80,
      "type": "text",
      "color": "1",
      "id": "3e31ec810812e7b7",
      "width": 250,
      "text": "[[Joseph]] obsesses over [[Cesare]]",
      "x": 1029
    },
    {
      "text": "",
      "id": "923acb02d83e4238",
      "height": 50,
      "width": 50,
      "x": 720,
      "type": "text",
      "y": -350
    },
    {
      "x": 4380,
      "type": "text",
      "id": "85e00043c3d388d3",
      "height": 94,
      "width": 230,
      "y": 764,
      "text": "[[Lucas]] is undercover listening to the discussion",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "0748736014548f5d",
      "y": 466,
      "color": "5",
      "height": 104,
      "x": 4555,
      "text": "[[Lucas]] wasn't here anymore when [[Isaac]] woke up",
      "width": 250
    },
    {
      "height": 50,
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4230,
      "text": "",
      "y": -545,
      "id": "34fae018f8df4e70",
      "width": 50
    },
    {
      "y": 1520,
      "height": 55,
      "type": "text",
      "text": "",
      "x": 5172,
      "id": "572e14fc790b5720",
      "width": 62
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3720,
      "text": "[[Isaac]], in a panic, hides under the seat and closes his eyes from fear.",
      "y": 747,
      "color": "1",
      "id": "4a9cc2c86b1dce10",
      "width": 250,
      "height": 126
    },
    {
      "text": "[[Isaac]] drops the coffee on purpose and as [[Cesare]] cleans up the mess, [[Isaac]] takes a pic of his genitals",
      "y": 1170,
      "height": 160,
      "color": "1",
      "width": 250,
      "type": "text",
      "id": "c49b521473c8c338",
      "x": 6540
    },
    {
      "height": 160,
      "type": "text",
      "width": 250,
      "id": "bf45ce2abe929050",
      "text": "They make up  and realize they might be more similar than they thought and decide to become partner in crime",
      "x": 7340,
      "y": 1530,
      "color": "1"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "width": 250,
      "id": "3a5491b3c9fb6788",
      "text": "[[Cesare]] does not find the force to go to the church and pretends to be sick",
      "x": 6478,
      "height": 122,
      "y": -500,
      "color": "3"
    },
    {
      "x": 6540,
      "y": 807,
      "width": 250,
      "id": "8d673242005669e4",
      "color": "2",
      "height": 106,
      "text": "[[Isaac]] tries to give the camera to [[Cesare]] but he refuses",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "text": "[[Cesare]] proposes and get to [[Isaac]] a coffee",
      "color": "3",
      "type": "text",
      "height": 60,
      "y": 936,
      "x": 6540,
      "id": "3043f2ad22451782",
      "width": 250
    },
    {
      "height": 106,
      "y": 1197,
      "id": "f51efa81dd0b0c92",
      "color": "3",
      "text": "[[Cesare]] gets really mad at [[Isaac]], grabs him and yells at him",
      "width": 250,
      "type": "text",
      "x": 7020
    },
    {
      "width": 250,
      "height": 60,
      "text": "Camera shatters on the ground",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 7425,
      "y": 1100,
      "color": "2",
      "id": "3a44141c093ff30a"
    },
    {
      "x": 7425,
      "height": 219,
      "text": "[[Isaac]] breaks down and admits he liked when [[Cesare]] exposed his genitals to him and when he took a pic of [him](Cesare) naked and wants to feel it again",
